{"data":[{"date":"07:09 01/08","title":"CLB Real Madrid c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i m\u1edbi v\u1ee5 Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/clb-real-madrid-co-dong-thai-moi-vu-hazard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CLB Real Madrid d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb b\u1ecf k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard c\u1ee7a Chelsea.</h2><h2>CLB Real Madrid s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1eeb b\u1ecf v\u1ee5 Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1eeb b\u1ecf v\u1ee5 Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1eeb b\u1ecf v\u1ee5 Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/28/Real-Madrid-muon-mua-Christian-Pulisic-voi-gia-70-trieu-euro-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ph\u00eda Real Madrid s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1eeb b\u1ecf v\u1ee5 Hazard</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi Ronaldo chia tay Real, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi Eden Hazard nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Bernabeu. Ba\u0309n th\u00e2n Eden Hazard cu\u0303ng ba\u0300y to\u0309 y\u0301 \u0111i\u0323nh gia nh\u00e2\u0323p Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n v\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 \u0111ang \u0111i v\u00e0o ng\u00f5 c\u1ee5t. T\u01a1\u0300 El Pais m\u01a1\u0301i \u0111\u00e2y \u0111a\u0303 ti\u00ea\u0301t l\u00f4\u0323 Los Blancos \u0111a\u0303 s\u0103\u0303n sa\u0300ng t\u01b0\u0300 bo\u0309 th\u01b0\u01a1ng vu\u0323 na\u0300y. Theo ba\u0301o chi\u0301 T\u00e2y Ban Nha,\u00a0K\u00ea\u0300n K\u00ea\u0300n Tr\u0103\u0301ng kh\u00f4ng s\u0103\u0303n sa\u0300ng \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u00f4\u0323t m\u01b0\u0301c gia\u0301 ky\u0309 lu\u0323c cho c\u00e2\u0300u thu\u0309 ng\u01b0\u01a1\u0300i Bi\u0309.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Chelsea t\u1eebng ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Hazard cho Real Madrid n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia s\u1edf h\u1eefu ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. Hi\u1ec7n HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111ang co\u0301 y\u0301 \u0111i\u0323nh trao chi\u00ea\u0301c b\u0103ng thu\u0309 qu\u00e2n cho Eden Hazard. B\u0103ng \u0111\u00f4\u0323i tr\u01b0\u01a1\u0309ng cu\u0309a The Blues \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u01a1\u0323c n\u0103\u0301m gi\u01b0\u0303 b\u01a1\u0309i trung v\u00ea\u0323 Gary Cahill.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Real, HLV Julen Lopetegui c\u0169ng \u0111ang ti\u0301nh \u0111\u00ea\u0301n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng a\u0301n kha\u0301c n\u00ea\u0301u kh\u00f4ng th\u00ea\u0309 chi\u00eau m\u00f4\u0323 Eden Hazard. Ca\u0301c ba\u0301o cho bi\u00ea\u0301t, HLV Julen Lopetegui \u0111a\u0303 g\u01b0\u0309i m\u00f4\u0323t ba\u0309n danh sa\u0301ch nh\u01b0\u0303ng ca\u0301i t\u00ean c\u00e2\u0300n mua cho ban la\u0303nh \u0111a\u0323o Los Blancos. Theo \u0111o\u0301, c\u01b0\u0323u thuy\u00ea\u0300n tr\u01b0\u01a1\u0309ng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00e2\u0300n th\u00eam m\u00f4\u0323t trung v\u00ea\u0323, m\u00f4\u0323t ti\u00ea\u0300n v\u00ea\u0323 va\u0300 m\u00f4\u0323t ti\u00ea\u0300n \u0111a\u0323o.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-18-sao-real-bat-ngo-muon-tro-thanh-doi-thu-cua-ronaldo-184-192440.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-18-sao-real-bat-ngo-muon-tro-thanh-doi-thu-cua-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-18-sao-real-bat-ngo-muon-tro-thanh-doi-thu-cua-ronaldo-184-192440.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 1/8: Sao Real b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nSao Real mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Pochettino \u201c\u0111\u00e1 xo\u00e1y\u201d Mourinho, \u2018H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u2019 Barca mu\u1ed1n gia nh\u1eadp M.U,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c c\u00f3 trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tu-bo-hazard-real-chi-70-trieu-euro-mua-sao-khung-dortmund-180-192424.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/9/tu-bo-hazard-real-chi-70-trieu-euro-mua-sao-khung-dortmund.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tu-bo-hazard-real-chi-70-trieu-euro-mua-sao-khung-dortmund-180-192424.html\">T\u1eeb b\u1ecf Hazard, Real chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Dortmund</span><br>\r\nReal Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Christian Pulisic, Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9 thay v\u00ec chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua Eden Hazard.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1860","checkdouble":"192441"},{"date":"08:12 01/08","title":"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Ronaldo \u1edf \u00dd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/chinh-thuc-nguoi-hung-world-cup-se-doi-dau-ronaldo-o-y.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Inter Milan ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Sime Vrsaljko t\u1eeb Atletico Madrid theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sime Vrsaljko l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0m n\u00ean <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/bai-hoc-tu-nguoi-croatia-dat-nuoc-nho-giac-mo-lon-421-191456.html\" target=\"_blank\">chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Croatia</span>. T\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng gi\u00fap h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf Atletico Madrid nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng, anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Sime Vrsaljko gia nh\u1eadp Inter Milan t\u1eeb Atletico Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Sime Vrsaljko gia nh\u1eadp Inter Milan t\u1eeb Atletico Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/chinh-thuc-nguoi-hung-world-cup-se-doi-dau-ronaldo-o-y.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Sime Vrsaljko gia nh\u1eadp Inter Milan t\u1eeb Atletico Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00f2a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi HLV Diego Simeone, Vrsaljko ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Wanda Metropolitano \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Inter Milan theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m. \u0110\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd \u201cthu\u00ea\u201d ng\u00f4i sao Croatia v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 6,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro, k\u00e8m theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t b\u1eb1ng 17,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7 Atletico Madrid: \u201cCLB ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Inter Milan trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Sime Vrsaljko. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t sau nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cSau hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 hy sinh cho CLB, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i xin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fac Sime m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 may m\u1eafn trong ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p ti\u1ebfp theo \u1edf Inter. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd s\u1ebd m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn mua \u0111\u1ee9t sau \u0111\u00e2y m\u1ed9t n\u0103m.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ea5t Vrsaljko nh\u01b0ng Atletico c\u0169ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf \u1edf h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Santiago Arias. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 26 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Wanda Metropolitano t\u1eeb PSV Eindhoven v\u00e0 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n 5 n\u0103m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/chinh-thuc-them-mot-ngoi-sao-cap-ben-la-liga-187-192018.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/chinh-thuc-them-mot-ngoi-sao-cap-ben-la-liga.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/chinh-thuc-them-mot-ngoi-sao-cap-ben-la-liga-187-192018.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn La Liga</span><br>\r\nCLB Atletico Madrid m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, Gelson Martins t\u1eeb CLB Sporting Lisbon...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1859","checkdouble":"192442"},{"date":"08:47 01/08","title":"Real Madrid c\u00f3 150 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eebng m\u01a1 Lewandowski","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/22/real-madrid-co-150-trieu-euro-cung-dung-mo-lewandowski.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Karl-Heinz Rummenigge kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Bayern Munich s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Real Madrid v\u1eabn t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i im h\u01a1i l\u1eb7ng ti\u1ebfng tr\u00ean phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, trong khi h\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/juventus-chieu-mo-cristiano-ronaldo-co-nhung-gia-tri-con-lon-hon-tien-176-191505.html\" target=\"_blank\">si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro</span>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern Munich kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Lewandowski cho Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Bayern Munich kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Lewandowski cho Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/22/real-madrid-co-150-trieu-euro-cung-dung-mo-lewandowski.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bayern Munich kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Lewandowski cho Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng Neymar, Kylian Mbappe, Eden Hazard hay Harry Kane \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Champions League t\u00ednh \u201cch\u1eefa ch\u00e1y\u201d b\u1eb1ng Robert Lewandowski, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng khi Lewandowski \u0111\u00e3 30 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ecf r\u00f5 \u00fd mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i khi m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi BL\u0110 Bayern Munich nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng, gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Karl-Heinz Rummenigge m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i \u201cH\u00f9m X\u00e1m x\u1ee9 Bavaria\u201d trong th\u1eadp ni\u00ean 70: \u201cV\u1edbi Robert, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai c\u1ea3 trong v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i CLB, r\u1eb1ng Bayern Munich l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb suy y\u1ebfu m\u1ed7i khi m\u00f9a h\u00e8 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd m\u1edf c\u1eeda ra v\u00ec n\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi c\u00f3 Robert trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh b\u1edfi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u00f3 100 hay 150 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb, Robert v\u1eabn s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-madrid-hazard-se-rat-on-nhung-thay-the-ronaldo-khong-180-191983.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/goc-real-madrid-hazard-se-rat-on-nhung-thay-the-ronaldo-khong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-madrid-hazard-se-rat-on-nhung-thay-the-ronaldo-khong-180-191983.html\">G\u00f3c Real Madrid: Hazard s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n, nh\u01b0ng thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo? Kh\u00f4ng!</span><br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV Julen Lopetegui s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n cung 50 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/m\u00f9a khi Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra \u0111i v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi Juventus, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1858","checkdouble":"192443"},{"date":"00:17 01/08","title":"Chelsea d\u00f9ng bom ti\u1ec1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/9/10/chelsea-dung-bom-tien-giu-chan-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Kante, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ef1c cao qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Kante</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN'Golo Kante l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i s\u1edf h\u1eefu n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111eo b\u00e1m dai d\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t tinh t\u1ebf trong nh\u1eefng pha v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef sao kh\u1ee7ng, Chelsea gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Kante h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef sao kh\u1ee7ng, Chelsea gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Kante h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/15/Quyet-tam-giu-sao-khung,-Chelsea-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-Kante-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kante</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111ang l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u00e0 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Kante kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Chelsea, song nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn v\u1eabn theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, h\u1ecd tin r\u1eb1ng chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Leicester.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-phap/tan-hlv-cua-psg-muon-rut-ruot-chelsea-197-184021.html\" target=\"_blank\">PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Kante</span>, Barca v\u00e0 Juventus c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. PSG th\u1eadm ch\u00ed s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Kante.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Kante</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Kante, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ef1c cao qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea v Swansea Kante va Fer\" title=\"Chelsea v Swansea Kante va Fer\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/29/chelsea-se-ban-kante-cho-psg-neu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea d\u00f9ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Kante</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd The Times, Chelsea d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 2 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Kante, \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean 290.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n. V\u1edbi m\u1ee9c\u00a0l\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Eden Hazard \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng cho Kante, Chelsea \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y tham v\u1ecdng gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i. HLV Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1, \u00f4ng c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Kante trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Kante s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Stamford Bridge v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Chelsea s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Man City trong tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, The Blues \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1857","checkdouble":"192430"},{"date":"00:40 01/08","title":"Barca chi 11 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd t\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/16/barca-chi-11-trieu-bang-mua-cai-ten-khong-the-ngo-toi-cua-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca s\u1ebd mua Simon Mignolet c\u1ee7a Liverpool trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Jasper Cillessen ra \u0111i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sky Sports \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cillessen c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jasper Cillessen kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf s\u00e2n Camp Nou. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Marc-Andre ter Stegen khi\u1ebfnc\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jasper Cillessen\" title=\"Jasper Cillessen\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/7/Chelsea-quan-tam-toi-thu-mon-Jasper-Cillessen--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jasper Cillessen c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a t\u1edbi, t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Barca, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca, hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jasper Cillessen, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid. Napoli c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan. C\u1ea3 Chelsea v\u00e0 Napoli \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca mua Mignolet thay Cillessen</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan Ra \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a TBN s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf. Barca s\u1ebd mua Simon Mignolet c\u1ee7a Liverpool trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Jasper Cillessen ra \u0111i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sky Sports \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 11 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Mignolet\" title=\"thu mon Mignolet\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/20/barca-bat-ngo-muon-ky-hop-dong-voi-hang-thai-cua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Mignolet</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/klopp-up-mo-kha-nang-tram-karius-va-mignolet-172-192217.html\" target=\"_blank\">Klopp c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Mignolet </span>c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Theo \u0111\u00f3, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Alisson khi\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi b\u1ecb h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Mignolet kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n r\u1eddi Liverpool. N\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Barca, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu t\u1edbi Camp Nou, Mignolet s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Marc-Andre ter Stegen. Ngo\u00e0i Barca th\u00ec Besiktas c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1856","checkdouble":"192432"},{"date":"01:08 01/08","title":"Yerry Mina n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU quan t\u00e2m?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/yerry-mina-noi-gi-khi-duoc-mu-quan-tam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n sinh t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong th\u00e1ng 8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>CLB Juventus tuy\u1ec3n sinh t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CLB Juventus tuy\u1ec3n sinh t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CLB Juventus tuy\u1ec3n sinh t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/37889006_411314022726153_7336238775078486016_n.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n Juventus b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u tuy\u1ec3n sinh t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00e0y 31-7 v\u1eeba qua, h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Juventus Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch tuy\u1ec3n sinh\u00a0kh\u00f3a \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Theo \u0111\u00f3, CLB l\u1eebng danh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 01/11/1897 t\u1ea1i Italia s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u00ed t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eeb B\u1eafc v\u00e0o Nam t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 10 t\u1edbi 19/8.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd l\u00e0 s\u1ebd x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea1i t\u1ec9nh B\u00e0 R\u1ecba - V\u0169ng T\u00e0u theo m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. H\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n Juventus Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o ra c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a CLB Juventus t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn, ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u0103m lo v\u1ec1 sinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, h\u1ecdc v\u0103n h\u00f3a, ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef v\u00e0 trang b\u1ecb c\u00e1c k\u0129 n\u0103ng s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft trong th\u1eddi gian tuy\u1ec3n sinh, CLB Juventus c\u1eed HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng H\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Juventus to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u \u2013 \u00f4ng Gianluca Settanni qua v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Ngo\u00e0i s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Gianluca Settanni, \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 HLV n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham gia tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn g\u1ed3m: HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1ed3ng S\u01a1n, HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh,\u2026<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ecbch tuy\u1ec3n sinh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n Juventus s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng: B\u00e0 R\u1ecba - V\u0169ng T\u00e0u (10-8), TP HCM (10 \u0111\u1ebfn 11-8), C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 (13-8), \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng (15-8), H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i (16 \u0111\u1ebfn 17-8), H\u00e0 T\u0129nh (19-8). \u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tuy\u1ec3n sinh c\u1ee7a CLB n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u00ed c\u00f3 n\u0103m sinh t\u1eeb 2006 \u2013 2009. C\u00e1c th\u00ed sinh c\u00f3 nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng tham gia d\u1ef1 thi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00ed qua s\u1ed1 hotline 0903 864 486, ho\u1eb7c fanpage Juventus Academy Vietnam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: robotoslab-regular, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1855","checkdouble":"192433"},{"date":"01:23 01/08","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Man City chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/chinh-thuc-man-city-chieu-mo-them-mot-tan-binh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man City mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Philippe Sandler, n\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m r\u01b0\u1ee1i v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao tr\u1ebb H\u00e0 Lan</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, trang ch\u1ee7 Man City x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad c\u00f3 th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. Man City mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Philippe Sandler, n\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m r\u01b0\u1ee1i v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Philippe Sandler t\u1eeb PEC Zwolle h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Man City mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Philippe Sandler t\u1eeb PEC Zwolle h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/chinh-thuc-man-city-chieu-mo-them-mot-tan-binh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Philippe Sandler</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrang ch\u1ee7 Man City th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o: \u201cMan City vui m\u1eebng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i k\u1ef9 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Philippe Sandler, hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n \u1edf Man City\u201d.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPhilippe Sandler sinh n\u0103m 1997, \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho CLB PEC Zwolle, \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 9 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 H\u00e0 Lan m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. Ng\u00f4i sao 21 tu\u1ed5i s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1 trung v\u1ec7, nh\u01b0ng khi c\u1ea7n anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan s\u1edf h\u1eefu chi\u1ec1u cao 1m88, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n, anh \u0111ang l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i U20 H\u00e0 Lan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 chuy\u00ean gia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Philippe Sandler l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 H\u00e0 Lan. \u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997, ch\u1ec9 trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Sandler Man City \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed t\u1eeb 2.5 \u0111\u1ebfn 3 tri\u1ec7u euro. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Man xanh, n\u1ebfu g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9i 1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan, Man City \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu trong tay m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1854","checkdouble":"192434"},{"date":"05:18 01/08","title":"HLV U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng h\u1ebft lo ng\u1ea1i sau 2 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0110N\u00c1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/7/22/hlv-u16-viet-nam-van-khong-het-lo-ngai-sau-2-thang-loi-lien-tiep-o-giai-dna.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0110T U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Campuchia \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 31/7, \u0110T U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Timor Leste v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm 4-0.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng h\u1ebft lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng h\u1ebft lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/22/hlv-u19-viet-nam-noi-gi-khi-lam-doc-co-cau-bai-tai-giai-u19-quoc-te.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm nh\u01b0ng U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng do k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Indonesia v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t ch\u01b0a y\u00ean t\u00e2m v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: &ldquo;Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i d\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng h\u00f4m nay c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, v\u1eabn c\u00f2n b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. L\u1ebd ra ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n. D\u1eabu sao t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p Indonesia \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, HLV tr\u01b0\u01a1ngr U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam cho bi\u1ebft:&nbsp;&ldquo;Tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chia \u0111\u1ec1u 50-50 cho c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eam l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 11 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i d\u00e8 ch\u1eebng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u00e2u d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U16 Indonesia s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 2/8 t\u1edbi.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-u16-viet-nam-40-u16-dong-timor-u16-dong-nam-a-2018-325-192404.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/video-tong-hop-u16-viet-nam-40-u16-dong-timor-u16-dong-nam-a-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-u16-viet-nam-40-u16-dong-timor-u16-dong-nam-a-2018-325-192404.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 4-0 U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor (U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018)</span><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 U16 Campuchia 1-0, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 g\u1eb7p U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1853","checkdouble":"192435"},{"date":"05:43 01/08","title":"CLB Juventus ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tuy\u1ec3n sinh t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/clb-juventus-chinh-thuc-tuyen-sinh-tai-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n sinh t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong th\u00e1ng 8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>CLB Juventus tuy\u1ec3n sinh t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CLB Juventus tuy\u1ec3n sinh t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CLB Juventus tuy\u1ec3n sinh t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/37889006_411314022726153_7336238775078486016_n.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n Juventus b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u tuy\u1ec3n sinh t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00e0y 31-7 v\u1eeba qua, h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Juventus Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch tuy\u1ec3n sinh\u00a0kh\u00f3a \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Theo \u0111\u00f3, CLB l\u1eebng danh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 01/11/1897 t\u1ea1i Italia s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u00ed t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eeb B\u1eafc v\u00e0o Nam t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 10 t\u1edbi 19/8.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd l\u00e0 s\u1ebd x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea1i t\u1ec9nh B\u00e0 R\u1ecba - V\u0169ng T\u00e0u theo m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. H\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n Juventus Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o ra c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a CLB Juventus t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn, ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u0103m lo v\u1ec1 sinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, h\u1ecdc v\u0103n h\u00f3a, ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef v\u00e0 trang b\u1ecb c\u00e1c k\u0129 n\u0103ng s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft trong th\u1eddi gian tuy\u1ec3n sinh, CLB Juventus c\u1eed HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng H\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Juventus to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u \u2013 \u00f4ng Gianluca Settanni qua v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Ngo\u00e0i s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Gianluca Settanni, \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 HLV n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham gia tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn g\u1ed3m: HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1ed3ng S\u01a1n, HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh,\u2026<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ecbch tuy\u1ec3n sinh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n Juventus s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng: B\u00e0 R\u1ecba - V\u0169ng T\u00e0u (10-8), TP HCM (10 \u0111\u1ebfn 11-8), C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 (13-8), \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng (15-8), H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i (16 \u0111\u1ebfn 17-8), H\u00e0 T\u0129nh (19-8). \u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tuy\u1ec3n sinh c\u1ee7a CLB n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u00ed c\u00f3 n\u0103m sinh t\u1eeb 2006 \u2013 2009. C\u00e1c th\u00ed sinh c\u00f3 nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng tham gia d\u1ef1 thi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00ed qua s\u1ed1 hotline 0903 864 486, ho\u1eb7c fanpage Juventus Academy Vietnam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: robotoslab-regular, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1852","checkdouble":"192436"},{"date":"06:02 01/08","title":"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tin x\u1ea5u v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/dt-olympic-viet-nam-don-them-mot-tin-xau-ve-nhan-su.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Nguy\u1ec5n Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng may g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018.</h2><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7&nbsp;Nguy\u1ec5n Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nguyen Trong Dai dinh chan thuong\" title=\"Nguy\u1ec5n Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/dt-olympic-viet-nam-don-them-mot-tin-xau-ve-nhan-su.png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u00e1t ng\u00e0y Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u qua 31/7, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a PVF. Sau nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng, HLV Park Hang Seo chia Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00e0nh 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 t\u1eadp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng may cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ngay \u0111\u1ea7u bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng may m\u1eafn khi b\u1ecb l\u1eadt c\u1ed5 ch\u00e2n&nbsp;\u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec nguy hi\u1ec3m. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, HLV Park Hang Seo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u b\u00e1c s\u0129 Choi - b\u00e1c s\u0129 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eebng \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb cho Tu\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Viettel r\u1eddi s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i ki\u1ec3m tra ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BHL U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o trong nay mai. Tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf v\u1edbi HLV Park Hang Seo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ki\u1ec3u n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 kho\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb 1 \u0111\u1ebfn 2 tu\u1ea7n m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. C\u00f2n nh\u1edb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng b\u1ecb t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 SLNA \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t kho\u1ea3ng 1 th\u00e1ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1851","checkdouble":"192437"},{"date":"06:17 01/08","title":"H\u1ed3ng Duy n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 ASIAD?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/hong-duy-noi-gi-sau-khi-mat-suat-du-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 ASIAD?</h2><h2>H\u1ed3ng Duy ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u00ec m\u1ea5t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 ASIAD</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Noi-kho-\u201cthu\u201d-va-\u201cdot\u201d-deu-phai-keu.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u1ed3ng Duy l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi ASIAD 2018 v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ed3ng Duy l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau khi anh g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y c\u1ea7n 1 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy cho hay: \"T\u00f4i bu\u1ed3n v\u00e0 kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo g\u1ecdi l\u00ean U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 ASIAD 2018 n\u00e0y m\u00ecnh ng\u1ed3i nh\u00e0\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i d\u00ednh ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u1ea5t h\u1ee5t h\u1eabng. T\u00f4i mong v\u00e0 ch\u00fac th\u1ea7y Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u1edf bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c chi\u1ec1u 28/07, sau m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c, H\u1ed3ng Duy \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00f9i \u1edf nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. G\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, H\u1ed3ng Duy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn t\u1ebf ki\u1ec3m tra v\u00e0 k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u00ecnh Ph\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ecb c\u0103ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f9i sau ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i. Ca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y kh\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-don-them-mot-tin-xau-ve-nhan-su-168-192437.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/dt-olympic-viet-nam-don-them-mot-tin-xau-ve-nhan-su.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-don-them-mot-tin-xau-ve-nhan-su-168-192437.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tin x\u1ea5u v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1</span><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Nguy\u1ec5n Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng may g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#222222;mso-fareast-language:ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1850","checkdouble":"192438"},{"date":"06:24 01/08","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (1/8/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-182018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 1/8 \u0111\u01b0